  "title": "Optional Internationalization practices",
  "contents": "\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"optional-internationalization-practices\">Optional Internationalization practices<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#optional-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p>The following optional topics help you manually configure the internationalization settings of your application.\nThe optional practices are meant for advanced or custom Angular applications.</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>To prepare your project for translations, you should have a basic understanding of the following subjects.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">Templates</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">Components</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> <a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">command-line</a> tool for managing the Angular development cycle</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> used for translation files</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\">Learn about optional Angular internationalization practices<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-optional-overview#learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n    <!-- Page removed; contents relocated to `i18n-optional-import-global-variants.md`\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-runtime-locale\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Set the runtime locale manually\">\n        <section>Set the runtime locale manually</section>\n        <p>Learn how to change the runtime locale for your project</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\">Set the runtime locale manually</p>\n    </a> \n    -->\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Import global variants of the locale data\">\n        <section>Import global variants of the locale data</section>\n        <p>Learn how to import locale data for language variants</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\">Import global variants of the locale data</p>\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Manage marked text with custom IDs\">\n        <section>Manage marked text with custom IDs</section>\n        <p>Learn how to implement custom IDs to help you manage your marked text</p>\n        <p class=\"card-footer\">Manage marked text with custom IDs</p>\n    </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">Last reviewed on Thu Aug 31 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#learn-about-optional-angular-internationalization-practices\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#optional-internationalization-practices\n - guide/i18n-optional-overview#prerequisites\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"
